# Agent operating rules + per-repo memory.
# Hard rule: NEVER commit CLAUDE.md / AGENTS.md / memory/ on any repo.
# These files carry operating discipline, mistakes log, and the
# verified-fact audit trail. They stay local to the working tree.
/CLAUDE.md
/AGENTS.md
/CONTEXT.md
/GEMINI.md
/WORKING.md
/SESSION_LOG.md
/memory/

# Internal strategy / architecture / design notes — NEVER commit.
# Public repo; this content includes risk-model and operational detail
# that should not be visible to adversaries or random readers.
/ARCHITECTURE.md
/PARSER-ARCHITECTURE.md
/MISTAKES.md
/STYLEGUIDE.md
/RISKS.md
/RUNBOOK.md
/NOTES.md
/TODO.md
/notes/
/internal/

