# Working-paper build artifacts — regenerable via `make paper` / `make zotero`.
# Source (papers.toml, *.qmd, *.typ, *.tex, *.bib, figures) is tracked; outputs are not.
research/working-papers/**/outputs/
research/working-papers/**/.quarto/
research/working-papers/**/*_files/
research/working-papers/**/*.pdf
research/working-papers/**/*.html
research/working-papers/_shared/zotero-sync.js
research/working-papers/_archive/

